        <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-800 mb-4">About the Shop Cart App</h1>
        <p class="text-lg text-gray-600 mb-6">
            The Shop Cart App is a user-friendly web application designed to simplify online shopping. It allows users to browse products, add items to their cart, and manage their shopping experience with ease. Built with modern web technologies, the app ensures a seamless and responsive interface for a delightful shopping experience.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-3">Key Features</h2>
        <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-gray-600 mb-6">
            <li><strong>Product Browsing</strong>: Explore a wide range of products with detailed descriptions and images.</li>
            <li><strong>Shopping Cart</strong>: Add, remove, and update items in your cart with real-time updates.</li>
            <li><strong>Responsive Design</strong>: Enjoy a consistent experience across desktops, tablets, and mobile devices.</li>
            <li><strong>Secure Checkout</strong>: Placeholder for secure payment processing (to be integrated with a payment gateway).</li>
            <li><strong>User-Friendly Interface</strong>: Intuitive navigation and clean design for effortless shopping.</li>
        </ul>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-3">Technology Stack</h2>
        <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-gray-600 mb-6">
            <li><strong>Frontend</strong>: React with Tailwind CSS for a dynamic and stylish user interface.</li>
            <li><strong>Backend</strong>: Placeholder for backend integration (e.g., Node.js, Express, or similar).</li>
            <li><strong>Deployment</strong>: Designed to be hosted on modern web platforms for scalability.</li>
        </ul>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-3">Purpose</h2>
        <p class="text-lg text-gray-600 mb-6">
            The Shop Cart App aims to provide a streamlined e-commerce solution for small to medium-sized businesses, offering a customizable platform to showcase products and engage customers effectively.
        </p>

